body_html: This is surprising -- you are compiling (by default) with -march=native. ​This means that unless you compile on a computer other than the one you run on, it should not use optimizations your machine doesn't understand. Did you set the optimization flags? Which hash are you building from?

body:
This is surprising -- you are compiling (by default) with
-march=native. ​This means that unless you compile on a computer other than
the one you run on, it should not use optimizations your machine doesn't
understand. Did you set the optimization flags? Which hash are you building
from?
